data.meta_description: 166 likes, 3 comments - parliament0f0wls on January 31, 2022: "Elliott Smith live at the Henry Fonda Theater in Los Angeles, California on January 31, 2003. Nineteen years ago today, I watched my hero, the late great Elliott Smith play for the very last time. This was my fifth time seeing him play and I feel so lucky and I am so thankful that I was alive and had the honor of being in his presence, to watch him play these gorgeous and heartbreakingly beautiful songs right before my ears and eyes.
